com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.node

Enum JsonNodeType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<JsonNodeType>
      • com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.node.JsonNodeType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<JsonNodeType>

    public enum JsonNodeType
extends Enum<JsonNodeType>
    Enumeration of JSON types. Covers all JSON types defined by RFC 4627 (array, boolean, null, number, object and string) but also Jackson-specific types: binary, missing and POJO; although does not distinguish between more granular types.
    Since:
    2.2
    See Also:
    BinaryNode, MissingNode, POJONode
